CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Maryland Medical Assistance Program – Coverage for the Treatment of
3 Obesity – Authorization
4 FOR the purpose of authorizing, beginning on a certain date, the Maryland Medical
5 Assistance Program to provide comprehensive coverage for the treatment of obesity;
6 requiring the Maryland Department of Health to provide notice to Program
7 recipients if the Department elects to provide the coverage; authorizing the
8 Maryland Department of Health to apply to the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid
9 Services for a State plan amendment authorizing the State to provide comprehensive
10 coverage for the treatment of obesity; and generally relating to the Maryland Medical
11 Assistance Program and coverage for the treatment of obesity.
12 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
13 Article – Health – General
14 Section 15–103(a)(1)
